{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"body":"Task triage round-2 (S2a/S2c/S5c now PASS+signed). Fixed the finer-grained blocks by pinning concrete values (per 'fully clarify now'):\n- REAL bug caught: the autoheal Docker socket must be mounted READ-WRITE (autoheal issues docker restart, a daemon write); my :ro would silently break restart. Corrected in S5a/S5d/S5.\n- S5a: pinned the volume name gerrit_autolander (via compose-up.sh gerrit_ prefix helper), the lockfile autolander.lock, and a concrete flock proving command.\n- S5b: resolved the rebase-on-behalf ACL concretely (no more 'verify at impl') — [access refs/heads/*] rebase = group Contributors in the rebar project.config; the on-behalf half needs no extra grant (checks the original uploader's existing push right); get_param (fail-fast); synthetic scratch-ref smoke change; named fallback on 403.\n- S5c (already passed): metric-based stuck alarm + AUTOLANDER_HANDBACK marker.\n- S5d: drain bounded to 120s + compose stop_grace_period: 120s (Docker's 10s default would SIGKILL before recovery.json is written); recovery rules for all 4 phases.\n- S5 story: pinned the stuck threshold (>45 min in a non-idle phase) + socket-rw note.\nRe-reviewing S5 + S5a/b/d."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783838811654748001,"uuid":"e6bd4e51-7e79-444f-b900-9b46dc3279be"}